'''鲨齿龙科'''（[[学名|学名]]：Carcharodontosauridae，意为“鲨鱼牙齿的蜥蜴”）是肉食性[[兽脚类|兽脚类]][[恐龙|恐龙]]的一个分类群，由[[恩斯特·斯特莫|恩斯特·斯特莫]]（Ernst Stromer）于1931年命名，在现代[[古生物学|古生物学]]中代表[[肉食龙类|肉食龙类]]的一个[[演化支|演化支]]。该科包含几种已知最大的陆地捕食者：[[南方巨兽龙|南方巨兽龙]]、[[马普龙|马普龙]]、[[鲨齿龙|鲨齿龙]]和[[魁纣龙|魁纣龙]]，它们的体型皆可与[[暴龙|暴龙]]匹敌甚至超过暴龙。克里斯托弗·亨德里克斯（Christophe Hendrickx）及其同事2015年发表的一篇论文中估计该科最大物种的最大身长为{{convert|14|m|ft}}，最小物种也至少有{{convert|6|m|ft}}长。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Hendrickx | first = Christophe | last2 = Hartman | first2 = Scott A. | last3 = Mateus | first3 = Octávio | year = 2015 | title = An Overview of Non-Avian Theropod Discoveries and Classification | journal = PalArch's Journal of Vertebrate Palaeontology | volume=12 | issue=1 | pages = 1–73}}</ref>

==演化==
[[File:Concavenator_Skull_diagram.svg|thumb]]颅骨重建]]
在[[白垩纪|白垩纪]]中前期，鲨齿龙科与[[棘龙科|棘龙科]]一样，是整个[[冈瓦纳古陆|冈瓦纳古陆]]上最大的掠食者，其成员亦分布在北美（[[高棘龙|高棘龙]]）、欧洲（[[昆卡猎龙|昆卡猎龙]]）和亚洲（[[假鲨齿龙|假鲨齿龙]]），<ref name=brusatteetal2009>{{cite journal | last1 = Brusatte | first1 = S. | last2 = Benson | first2 = R. | last3 = Chure | first3 = D. | last4 = Xu | first4 = X. | last5 = Sullivan | first5 = C. | last6 = Hone | first6 = D. | year = 2009 | title = The first definitive carcharodontosaurid (Dinosauria: Theropoda) from Asia and the delayed ascent of tyrannosaurids | url = https://www.pure.ed.ac.uk/ws/files/8232136/PDF_Brusatteetal2009FirstDefinitiveCarcharodontosaurid.pdf| journal = Naturwissenschaften | volume =  96| issue = 9| pages =  1051–8| doi = 10.1007/s00114-009-0565-2 | pmid = 19488730 | bibcode = 2009NW.....96.1051B | hdl = 20.500.11820/33528c2e-0c9c-4160-8693-984f077ee5d0 | s2cid = 25532873 | hdl-access = free }}</ref>生存时期贯穿1.27～1.21亿年前的[[巴列姆阶|巴列姆阶]]至9300～8900万年前的[[土仑阶|土仑阶]]，土仑阶过后被冈瓦纳古陆上较小的[[阿贝力龙科|阿贝力龙科]]及北美和亚洲的[[暴龙科|暴龙科]]所取代。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|date=2021-09-01|title=Testing the persistence of Carcharodontosauridae (Theropoda) in the Upper Cretaceous of Patagonia based on dental evidence|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0195667121001221|journal=Cretaceous Research|language=en|volume=125|pages=104875|doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2021.104875|issn=0195-6671|last1=Meso|first1=J.G.|last2=Juárez Valieri|first2=R.D.|last3=Porfiri|first3=J.D.|last4=Correa|first4=S.A.S.|last5=Martinelli|first5=A.G.|last6=Casal|first6=G.A.|last7=Canudo|first7=J.I.|last8=Poblete|first8=F.|last9=Dos Santos|first9=D.}}</ref><ref name="novasetal2005">{{Cite journal|first1=Fernando E.|last1=Novas|first2=Silvina|last2=de Valais|first3=Patrick|last3=Vickers-Rich|first4=Tom|last4=Rich|year=2005|title=A large Cretaceous theropod from Patagonia, Argentina, and the evolution of carcharodontosaurids|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=92|pages=226–230|doi=10.1007/s00114-005-0623-3}}</ref>[[巴西|巴西]][[马斯特里赫特阶|马斯特里赫特阶]]沉积层中发现过疑似鲨齿龙科的牙齿及[[上颌骨|上颌骨]]，<ref name=Azevedoetal2013>{{cite journal |author=Rodrigo P. Fernandes de Azevedo |author2=Felipe Medeiros Simbras |author3=Miguel Rodrigues Furtado |author4=Carlos Roberto A. Candeiro |author5=Lílian Paglarelli Bergqvist |name-list-style=amp|year=2013 |title=First Brazilian carcharodontosaurid and other new theropod dinosaur fossils from the Campanian–Maastrichtian Presidente Prudente Formation, São Paulo State, southeastern Brazil |journal=Cretaceous Research |volume=40 |pages=131–142 |doi=10.1016/j.cretres.2012.06.004}}</ref><ref name=Candeiroetal2012>{{cite journal|author1=Carlos Roberto Candeiro |author2=Philip Currie |author3=Lílian Bergqvist |year=2012 |title=Theropod teeth from the Marília Formation (late Maastrichtian) at the Paleontological Site of Peirópolis in Minas Gerais State, Brazil |journal=Revista Brasileira de Geociências |volume=42 |issue=2 |pages=323–330 |doi=10.5327/z0375-75362012000200008 |doi-access=free }}</ref>但后来经重新检查后归入阿贝力龙科，<ref name="2017brazicarch">{{cite journal | last1 = Delcourt | first1 = R. | last2 = Grillo | first2 = O.N. | title = Carcharodontosaurids remained extinct in the Campanian-Maastrichtian: Reassessment of a fragmentary maxilla from Presidente Prudente Formation, Brazil | journal = Cretaceous Research | volume = 84 | pages = 515–524 | date = 2017 | doi = 10.1016/j.cretres.2017.09.008 }}</ref>而且土仑阶结束后的南美洲并没有该科的可靠记录。<ref name=":0" />2011年12月，奥利弗·劳赫（Oliver W. M. Rauhut）描述[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]东南{{le|敦达古鲁组|Tendaguru Formation}}[[晚侏罗世|晚侏罗世]]（约1.54～1.5亿年前的[[启莫里阶|启莫里阶]]晚期至[[提通阶|提通阶]]早期）一新属和新种米氏[[旧鲨齿龙|旧鲨齿龙]]，该属代表已知最古老的鲨齿龙科。<ref name=Veterupristisaurus>{{cite journal |last=Rauhut |first=Oliver W. M. |year=2011 |title=Theropod dinosaurs from the Late Jurassic of Tendaguru (Tanzania) |journal=Special Papers in Palaeontology |volume=86 |pages=195–239 |url=https://www.palass.org/publications/special-papers-palaeontology/archive/86/article_pp195-239}}</ref>

==分类==
鲨齿龙科最初由[[恩斯特·斯特莫|恩斯特·斯特莫]]于1931年命名以包含新种撒哈拉鲨齿龙，1995年描述鲨齿龙近亲南方巨兽龙时亦将其归入该科，此外还有很多古生物学家将[[高棘龙|高棘龙]]归入该科（塞里诺等人，1996年；哈里斯，1998年；霍兹，2000年；劳赫，2003年；艾迪与克拉克，2011年；劳赫，2011年），但也有人将其归入近缘的[[异特龙科|异特龙科]]（柯里和卡彭特，2000年；科里亚和柯里，2002年）。鲨齿龙科的鉴别特征包括：①前颌齿间板的背腹深度超过前后宽度的两倍；②齿骨前端呈次矩形；③牙釉质表面粗糙；④前颌骨有四个齿槽，高度大于侧面长度；⑤后凹型颈椎的神经棘高度超过椎体的1.9倍；⑥泪骨和由颅顶形成并构成宽阔眶架的眶后骨上存在大量有纹理的褶皱；⑦股骨头近端倾斜。<ref name="conca">{{cite journal | last1 = Ortega | first1 =  F. | last2 = Escaso | first2 = F. | last3 = Sanz | first3 = J. L. | date = 2010 | title = A bizarre, humped Carcharodontosauria (Theropoda) from the Lower Cretaceous of Spain | journal = Nature | volume = 467 | issue =  7312 | pages = 203–206 | doi = 10.1038/nature09181 | url = http://pagina.jccm.es/museociencias/Ortega_etal_2010_Tero_Concavenator_Ki_Cuenca_esp_nature09181.pdf | pmid=20829793| bibcode = 2010Natur.467..203O | s2cid = 4395795 }}</ref><ref name="acrocr">{{cite journal | last1 = Eddy | first1 = DR | last2 = Clarke | first2 = JA | date = 2011 | title = New Information on the Cranial Anatomy of ''Acrocanthosaurus atokensis'' and Its Implications for the Phylogeny of Allosauroidea (Dinosauria: Theropoda) | journal = PLOS ONE | volume = 6 | issue = 3 | pages = e17932 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0017932 | pmid=21445312 | pmc=3061882| bibcode = 2011PLoSO...617932E | doi-access = free }}</ref>2006年发现马普龙以后，{{le|罗多尔夫·科里亚|Rodolfo Coria}}（Rodolfo Coria）和{{le|菲力·柯里|Phil Currie}}（Phil Currie）建立了南方巨兽龙亚科以包含最衍生的南美物种，这些物种之间的关系较之与非洲及欧洲物种的关系更为密切。科里亚和柯里没有正式将魁纣龙归入该亚科，等待对该属进行更详细的描述，但指出从股骨特征来看，魁纣龙可能也是该亚科的成员。<ref name="coria&currie2006">{{cite journal | last1 = Coria | first1 = R.A. | last2 = Currie | first2 = P.J. | year = 2006 | title = A new carcharodontosaurid (Dinosauria, Theropoda) from the Upper Cretaceous of Argentina | journal = Geodiversitas | volume = 28 | issue = 1| pages = 71–118 }}</ref>
[[File:Carcharodontosaurid_scale.svg|thumb]]
1998年，{{le|保罗·塞里诺|Paul Sereno}}（Paul Sereno）将该科定义为：由鲨齿龙及与其关系近于[[异特龙|异特龙]]、[[中华盗龙|中华盗龙]]、[[单脊龙|单脊龙]]或[[冰脊龙|冰脊龙]]的所有物种构成的[[演化支|演化支]]。根据定义，该演化支不属于[[异特龙科|异特龙科]]。

